result:
<!-- 编辑弹框 -->
    <a-modal
    title="编辑"
    style="top: 20px;"
    :width="600"
    v-model="visible"
    @ok="handleSubmit"
        v-preventReClick
  :destroyOnClose="true"
  :maskClosable = "false"
  >
  <a-form :form="form">
    <a-form-item
      label="版本描述"
      :labelCol="labelCol"
      :wrapperCol="wrapperCol">
      <a-textarea
        placeholder="请输入描述" :rows="4"
        v-decorator="[
          'contents',
          {
            rules: [{message: '请输入版本描述' }],
            initialValue: editData.contents,
          }]"
        />
    </a-form-item>
  </a-form>
  </a-modal>
